# This configuration file provides parameters for the devops script.
# The values are read in order, so please ensure the order is maintained.

# Name of the user responsible for DevOps tasks.
CodeApprover

# Email of the user responsible for DevOps tasks.
pucfada@pm.me

# The project name, usually coinciding with the repository name.
